MODIFICATIONS AND ENHANCEMENTS

The following substantial modifications have been made to the original work:

- Complete reimplementation of core architecture for Web3 integration
- Addition of autonomous agent capabilities and intent recognition
- Integration with 160+ DeFi protocols via Enso Network
- Implementation of embedded wallet infrastructure via Privy
- Development of natural language to on-chain action translation
- Creation of portfolio management and strategy execution engine
- Addition of real-time yield optimization algorithms
- Multi-chain support and cross-protocol orchestration

These modifications represent a fundamental transformation of the original
codebase into a specialized platform for autonomous Web3 financial agents.

